summary: Comprehensive documentation of all 8 MezTal Relume projects showing that only 2 are viable (MezTa 8 with 30-35 pages and MezTal 5 with 25-30 pages), 4 are empty/corrupted (MezTal 3, 4, 6, 7), and 2 need further investigation (MezTal 1, 2 likely flat structure). Includes full sitemap extract for MezTal 5, summary of MezTa 8 from previous export, technical notes about API rate limiting, and recommendation to proceed with MezTa 8 as the most complete option.
